CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 25, 1960, pg. A11 reads: "9. Nutrilite Products Inc. demonstrated the art of healthful make-up by Blondeva Wharton, demonstrator. Others shown are model Gaynelle Crosby, New York visitor; Mabel Rodgers, local distributor; Ernest E. Greco, key distributor, and sponsors Lue and Sue Schohn."
TitMainTitle: Group of men and women including Blondeva Wharton, Gaynelle Crosby, Mabel Rodgers, Ernest E. Greco, Lue and Sue Schohn gathered in Nutrilite Food Supplement booth in Syria Mosque for the 1960 Courier-WAMO Home-A-Rama
